== Kinetic Core Format Answers
Formats a Kinetic Core Submission's answers.

=== Parameters
[SpaceSlug]
  The Space slug to be searched. If this value is not entered, the
  Space slug will default to the one configured in info values.
[Submission ID]
    The id of the submission to format answers for.

=== Sample Configuration
Submission ID::				d3ab56e0-b584-11e5-8783-ddc68221c3ba

=== Results
[XML of results]
<results format="xml">
        <result name="### Placeholder for field name ###"/>
</results>

=== Detailed Description
Builds an XML of the fields on the form. For example, if the form held two fields, color and size, 
the response might look like this:

<results format="xml">
	<result name="color">Red</result>
	<result name="size">Small</result>
</results>